==English==

=== Adjective ===
'''ambivalent'''
# [[Simultaneously]] feeling opposing or [[contradictory]] feelings.
# Having two opposite or conflicting feelings simultaneously

''Thesaurus'': vacillating, inconsistent, of two minds, fluctuating, unresolved, warring, wavering, conflicted, confused, unsettled, unsure, mixed.


